{"tid":1020872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"土瓜灣印傭被咬傷嘴　學校職員報警拘16歲男生","createTime":"2019-02-14T01:32:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T01:57:05.000Z","uid":6497,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"17c584640df8a35092a98a41820a9d784cce675e","tid":1020872,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T01:32:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2434859/org/a9dc98632d97baabbf60690f764c39d1.jpg/trQKI_sd5OY-g1VKb22JP89Vpyhz1anG_5mY0_-ZmNM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2434859%2Forg%2Fa9dc98632d97baabbf60690f764c39d1.jpg%2FtrQKI_sd5OY-g1VKb22JP89Vpyhz1anG_5mY0_-ZmNM&h=e4d6221d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n13日(周三)早上11時許，警方接獲土瓜灣浙江街一間學校的職員報案，指一名外傭在校內，懷疑被一名男學生，用手及口襲擊受傷。警方接報後，將案件暫列「發現懷疑精神紊亂人士」，並派員前往跟進。警員接報到場經初步調查，即場拘捕一名16歲男學生，涉嫌「襲擊致造成實際身體傷害」，案件交由九龍城警區刑事調查隊跟進。至於該名44歲印尼籍女傭，因嘴部受傷，由救護車清醒送往伊利沙伯醫院治理。警方正調查事件。"},{"pid":"ae40a8b2cc11c9b248657b557a0dcc0ba6abfda9","tid":1020872,"uid":209487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T01:32:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"23fc08c1b1b6c1c5a1dde8f7c29c919b529fb1b5","tid":1020872,"uid":209487,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T01:33:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8de5dac17a7c99b068c96dc5b892b77f0d992b49","tid":1020872,"uid":10905,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T01:34:10.000Z","msg":"發現傻人案有新名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"207624a28e227056ebae6e292e02c81d23f868fb","tid":1020872,"uid":70398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T01:35:43.000Z","msg":"咬佢個嘴<br />\n係咪即係。。。"},{"pid":"cf3a40b50af15127249588e962bb108aa6e13e2c","tid":1020872,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T01:36:56.000Z","msg":"要咬傷個嘴一定打車輪打得好撚勁先做到"},{"pid":"48865f0f9dd680e5f8381769dfb82c5f41d38c1c","tid":1020872,"uid":21423,"like":2,"di